policies.content: Note that if canceled, modified, or in case of no-show, the total price of the reservation will be charged. If you don’t show up you will be charged the total price of the reservation.

All children are welcome. One child under 3 years stays free of charge in a crib.
One child under 7 years stays free of charge when using existing beds.
One child from 7 to 12 years is charged VND 100000  per night when using existing beds.
One child from 12 to 13 years is charged VND 200000  per night when using existing beds.
There is no capacity for extra beds in the room.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 4.
The maximum number of cribs in a room is 1.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in all areas and is free of charge.
Free private parking is available  on site (reservation is needed).
Pets are not allowed.
You'll be charged a prepayment of the total price at any time.
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
